text: Coptaspis is a genus of bush crickets in the tribe Agraeciini, containing the following species: *Coptaspis brevipennis Redtenbacher, 1891 *Coptaspis crassinervosa Redtenbacher, 1891 *Coptaspis elegans Willemse, 1966 *Coptaspis lateralis Erichson, 1842 == References == == External links == * Category:Conocephalinae Category:Tettigoniidae genera
title: Coptaspis
